  "detailed_description": "<h1>More from us</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/94c81e2dcbd97a448a521c9781eed74b.poster.avif?t=1722517971\" width=596 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/94c81e2dcbd97a448a521c9781eed74b.webm?t=1722517971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/94c81e2dcbd97a448a521c9781eed74b.mp4?t=1722517971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make your way through 25 levels of increasing difficulty by manipulating physics to your advantage, shooting force fields to slow down or speed yourself up and the environment!<br><br><strong>Tired of easy games?</strong> Hop into the Competitive and Speedrun modes to climb the leaderboards! Challenge your friends, online players and yourself! Be prepared... It's not going to be easy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fast-paced platformer in first-person experience!<br></li><li> Challenging levels providing hours of gameplay<br></li><li> Story Mode with an intriguing science-fiction story filled with funny dialogues<br></li><li> Competitive Mode with Steam leaderboards to challenge the world ...and your friends<br></li><li> Speedrun Mode with an in-game timer for players looking for the hardest of challenges!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/1c4d193f2f7f12386d71659217cbe323.poster.avif?t=1722517971\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/1c4d193f2f7f12386d71659217cbe323.webm?t=1722517971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/1c4d193f2f7f12386d71659217cbe323.mp4?t=1722517971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/94c81e2dcbd97a448a521c9781eed74b.poster.avif?t=1722517971\" width=596 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/94c81e2dcbd97a448a521c9781eed74b.webm?t=1722517971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/94c81e2dcbd97a448a521c9781eed74b.mp4?t=1722517971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make your way through 25 levels of increasing difficulty by manipulating physics to your advantage, shooting force fields to slow down or speed yourself up and the environment!<br><br><strong>Tired of easy games?</strong> Hop into the Competitive and Speedrun modes to climb the leaderboards! Challenge your friends, online players and yourself! Be prepared... It's not going to be easy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fast-paced platformer in first-person experience!<br></li><li> Challenging levels providing hours of gameplay<br></li><li> Story Mode with an intriguing science-fiction story filled with funny dialogues<br></li><li> Competitive Mode with Steam leaderboards to challenge the world ...and your friends<br></li><li> Speedrun Mode with an in-game timer for players looking for the hardest of challenges!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/1c4d193f2f7f12386d71659217cbe323.poster.avif?t=1722517971\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811270/extras/1c4d193f2f7f12386d71659217cbe323.webm?t=1722517971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a